> He flew off with Drillbit towards the base sinking his claws in JUST

>

{Grimlock}

    The dinobot arrives just as Sunhawk streaks by carrying another
prisoner, looking around at the fallen preds he stomps over to where Inferno
lays, raising a large metal foot he kicks the downed bot once or twice, "Me
Grimlock say you wake up now. Grimlock not carrying your slagged skidplate
back to base if pred bot can walk. Me Grimlock says me not labour bot, me
king!"
